item.title: Reverse Proxying Attacker Tools
item.author: Rob Fuller
item.description: Ever want to have all of your C2 go to the same box, have the functionality of Meterpreter, and Empire, while making it so if anyone goes to the actual site of your C2 all they get is something like Google?
